# Frontend Architecture вЂ” Last-Mile Delivery Platform

A production-grade React frontend for a microservices delivery platform, inspired by Swiggy/Zomato aesthetics.

---

## Backend Services Reference

| Service | Port | Base Path | Key Endpoints |
|---|---|---|---|
| **API Gateway** | 8080 | `/` | Routes all traffic, JWT validation |
| **User Service** | 8081 | `/api/auth` | `POST /register`, `POST /login` |
| **Order Service** | 8081 | `/api/orders` | `POST /`, `GET /`, `PATCH /{id}/assign`, `PATCH /{id}/status` |
| **Driver Service** | 8082 | `/api/drivers` | `POST /register`, `PATCH /{id}/status`, `PATCH /{id}/location`, `POST /{id}/gps`, `GET /available`, `POST /{dId}/orders/{oId}/pickup`, `POST /{dId}/orders/{oId}/delivered` |
| **Logistics Service** | 8083 | вЂ” | Kafka-driven auto-assignment (no REST API) |
| **Tracking Service** | 8084 | `/tracking` | `GET /{driverId}` (Redis location) |
| **Notification Service** | 8086 | `/ws/notify` | WebSocket broadcast |

**Kafka Topics:** `order-created`, `driver-assigned`, `order-picked-up`, `order-delivered`

**Order Statuses:** `PENDING` в†’ `ASSIGNED` в†’ `PICKED_UP` в†’ `DELIVERED` / `CANCELLED`

**User Roles:** `CUSTOMER`, `DRIVER`, `ADMIN`

---

## 1. Tech Stack

| Layer | Choice | Why |
|---|---|---|
| **Framework** | React 18 + Vite | Blazing-fast HMR, ESM-native, lightweight |
| **Routing** | React Router v6 | Nested layouts, role-based guards |
| **State** | Zustand | Minimal boilerplate, no Provider nesting, perfect for this scale |
| **HTTP Client** | Axios | Interceptors for JWT injection + refresh |
| **WebSocket** | Native [WebSocket](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/OneDrive/Desktop/6th%20sem/delivery%20system%20project/delivery-system-microservices/notification-service/src/main/java/com/example/notification_service/config/WebSocketConfig.java#9-24) API | Backend uses raw WS at `/ws/notify`, not STOMP/SockJS |
| **Maps** | React Leaflet + OpenStreetMap | Free, no API key required, production-quality |
| **Styling** | CSS Modules + CSS Custom Properties | No build tooling overhead, full control over design tokens |
| **Animations** | Framer Motion | React-native spring physics, layout animations |
| **Icons** | Lucide React | Crisp, consistent SVG icon library |
| **Toasts** | React Hot Toast | Lightweight, customizable notification popups |
| **Geocoding** | OpenStreetMap Nominatim | Free address в†” coords conversion |

