## 3. Pages & User Flows

### 3.1 Authentication Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as React App
    participant GW as API Gateway :8080
    participant US as User Service

    U->>FE: Enter email + password + role
    FE->>GW: POST /api/auth/login
    GW->>US: Forward (public path, no JWT needed)
    US-->>GW: JWT token string
    GW-->>FE: JWT token
    FE->>FE: Store JWT in localStorage + Zustand
    FE->>FE: Decode JWT в†’ extract role
    FE->>FE: Route to Customer or Driver dashboard
```

### 3.2 Customer Pages

| Page | Description | Key Features |
|---|---|---|
| **Login / Register** | Auth with role selection (Customer/Driver) | Animated form transitions, validation |
| **Customer Dashboard** | Overview with recent orders + stats | Animated stat cards, order count, active deliveries |
| **Place Order** | Form with pickup & delivery address | Address autocomplete (Nominatim), map preview, animated submit |
| **My Orders** | Filterable list of all orders | Status badges, timeline, click-to-track |
| **Track Order** | Live map showing driver location | Real-time Leaflet map, animated marker, ETA display, status stepper |

### 3.3 Driver Pages

| Page | Description | Key Features |
|---|---|---|
| **Driver Dashboard** | Toggle availability, see assigned orders | Online/Offline toggle, GPS broadcasting, earning stats |
| **Active Delivery** | Current delivery with navigation | Live map with route, pickup/delivered buttons, order details |
| **Order History** | Past completed deliveries | Completed/cancelled filter, delivery timeline |

