## 6. State Management (Zustand)

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[authStore] -->|token, user, role| B[ProtectedRoute]
    C[orderStore] -->|orders, activeOrder| D[MyOrdersPage]
    C -->|activeOrder| E[TrackOrderPage]
    F[driverStore] -->|isOnline, assignedOrders| G[DriverDashboard]
    H[notificationStore] -->|notifications| I[NotificationBell]
    J[WebSocket] -->|events| C
    J -->|events| H
```

| Store | State | Actions |
|---|---|---|
| `authStore` | `token`, `user`, `role`, `isAuthenticated` | [login()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/OneDrive/Desktop/6th%20sem/delivery%20system%20project/delivery-system-microservices/user-service/src/main/java/com/vijay/user_service/controller/AuthController.java#18-23), [register()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/OneDrive/Desktop/6th%20sem/delivery%20system%20project/delivery-system-microservices/driver-service/src/main/java/com/vijay/driver_service/controller/DriverController.java#24-28), `logout()`, `hydrateFromStorage()` |
| `orderStore` | `orders[]`, `activeOrder`, `loading` | `fetchOrders()`, [placeOrder()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/OneDrive/Desktop/6th%20sem/delivery%20system%20project/delivery-system-microservices/order-service/src/main/java/com/vijay/order_service/controller/OrderController.java#20-25), `updateOrderFromWS()` |
| `driverStore` | `isOnline`, `assignedOrders[]`, `currentLocation` | [toggleStatus()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/OneDrive/Desktop/6th%20sem/delivery%20system%20project/delivery-system-microservices/driver-service/src/main/java/com/vijay/driver_service/controller/DriverController.java#29-33), [sendGps()](file:///c:/Users/ASUS/OneDrive/Desktop/6th%20sem/delivery%20system%20project/delivery-system-microservices/driver-service/src/main/java/com/vijay/driver_service/controller/DriverController.java#41-49), `markPickup()`, `markDelivered()` |
| `notificationStore` | `notifications[]`, `unreadCount` | `addNotification()`, `markAllRead()`, `clearAll()` |

