## 7. Map Integration (React Leaflet)

### 7.1 Live Tracking Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    A[Driver App] -->|POST /drivers/{id}/gps| B[Driver Service]
    B -->|Kafka: gps-events| C[Tracking Service]
    C -->|Store| D[(Redis)]
    E[Customer App] -->|Poll GET /tracking/{driverId}| C
    C -->|"lat,lng"| E
    E -->|Update marker| F[Leaflet Map]
```

### 7.2 Key Implementation Details

- **Polling interval**: Every 3 seconds via `useDriverLocation` hook
- **Animated markers**: Smooth CSS transition between GPS coordinates (no jumps)
- **Route visualization**: Polyline from pickup в†’ current в†’ delivery coordinates
- **Map tiles**: OpenStreetMap free tiles вЂ” `https://{s}.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png`
- **Geocoding**: Nominatim API to convert addresses to lat/lng for map positioning

