## 9. Animations & UX Enhancements

### 9.1 Framer Motion Animations

| Where | Animation |
|---|---|
| Page transitions | Fade + slide-up with `AnimatePresence` |
| Order cards | `layout` animation for list reordering |
| Status badge | Color morph transition on status change |
| Dashboard stats | Count-up number animation on mount |
| Map marker | Spring-physics interpolation between GPS points |
| Form validation | Shake animation on error |
| Buttons | Scale-down on press + ripple effect |
| Sidebar | Smooth slide-in/out on mobile |
| Toast notifications | Slide-in from top-right with auto-dismiss |
| Order timeline | Staggered step reveal animation |

### 9.2 Micro-Interactions

- **Online/Offline toggle**: Smooth slider with color transition + particle burst
- **Order placed**: Success confetti animation + toast
- **Driver assigned**: Pulse ring around driver avatar
- **Delivery complete**: Checkmark lottie-style animation
- **Hover effects**: Cards lift 4px with box-shadow spread, navbar items underline slide

