## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **JWT Secret Key Mismatch**: The user-service uses `"vijay-super-secret-jwt-key-2026-delivery-system"` while the API gateway uses `"mySecretKeymySecretKey..."`. These MUST match for JWT validation to work end-to-end. This needs to be fixed in the backend before the frontend can work properly through the gateway.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Gateway Routing Incomplete**: Currently only `order-service` has an explicit route in the gateway. Routes for `driver-service`, `user-service`, and `tracking-service` should be added. The Eureka discovery locator is enabled (`lower-case-service-id=true`), so services may be accessible via `/{service-name}/...` pattern, but explicit routes would be more reliable.

> [!NOTE]
> The notification WebSocket endpoint (`ws://localhost:8086/ws/notify`) is direct to the notification service, bypassing the gateway. This is fine for development but in production should be proxied.

